        "authors": "Neeltje van Doremalen;Alexandra Sch\u00e4fer;Vineet D. Menachery;Michael Letko;Trenton Bushmaker;Robert J. Fischer;Dania M. Figueroa;Patrick W. Hanley;Greg Saturday;Ralph S. Baric;Vincent J. Munster",
