        "authors": "Wan Beom Park;Nak-Jung Kwon;Su-Jin Choi;Chang Kyung Kang;Pyoeng Gyun Choe;Jin Yong Kim;Jiyoung Yun;Gir-Won Lee;Moon-Woo Seong;Nam Joong Kim;Jeong-Sun Seo;Myoung-don Oh",
